node.text: Proper fall vibes - crispy air, ice cold water and low sun!!🤩🔥🧡 it smells soooo good outside now,! Not sure what it is- but it's so fresh😂 anyone else who notice the fresh smell of fall?☀️🍂🍁 hows the water temperature where you at? #Norway #Fall #Gopro

node.text: I'm not the biggest fan of fall season- but when it looks like THIS!??😭😍♥️ wow!! It was full overcast downtown so I decided to drive up the hill across the lake- it was definitely worth it🤩 if you live in a valley and it's low clouds- always make sure to get higher up to see how it looks like above the clouds🤩 what do you think?? #Norway #Gopro #Fall

node.text: First night in Harstad was unreal😍🌸 weather forecast said rain and wind, but as we arrived at our camp for the night we were blessed with northern lights and a sky full of stars😭✨💫☄️ and on top of that we got to sleep in an igloo made of glass! Hard to fall asleep when the lights keep going above you!! This is at @arcticseatosummits btw- a completely private sleepover igloo with your very own island and swimming spot! Can't recommend it enough- felt like a princess sleeping out there😂🌸 now it's time for Lofoten!🏄🏼‍♀️ #Norway #Northernlights #Aurora

node.text: AD @samsungnorge💙 Summer has come to an end, so I wanted to do a little post with photos and shots from my Samsung lens!🤩 What a summer it has been, and I love looking back at the photos. Six of them are taken with the wide lens and two of them with portrait mode (the ones with blurry background). Which one did you like the most?😍🌼📸 there's more to see on my story! ps. The model is Samsung Galaxy Ultra 21! #withGalaxy #TeamGalaxy

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by KAROLINE FOSSE on September 05, 2021. May be an image of 1 person, child, standing, sky and ocean.

node.text: I KNOW it's a bit early to be excited for winter, but LOOK AT THIS!?🤩😭💙 I'm headed up north next week and that got me thinking about the winter 19/20 I stayed and worked at @lofotenpanorama 🥰 so here's a Lofoten winter throwback! Is it too early to be excited for winter?😇 I'm not a big fall-person, so the quicker the snow comes, the better😁 #Norway #Gopro #Lofoten

node.text:
Always fun playing around😁💦it's been weeks without rain so hard to find any water on the roads these days🙊 this photo is shot with an 85mm lens with 1.8 aperture and 1/2000 shutter! Important with a quickkkk shutter IF you want that super crisp water splash🤩 could probably be cool with a low shutter as well, gonna try that next time🙌🏼 swipe to see what a quick shutter can do☺️ 
Do people know what I mean when I say 85mm 1.8 aperture 1/2000 shutter? Or is it like a weird language? Should I try to explain through story? Let me know:) #Norway #Phototips #Summer

node.text: A sunset for the books😍🌅♥️ this is in Vestkapp- all the way west in Norway! What a beautiful place with a 360 view over the ocean, mountains and islands! Best part is that you can drive aaall the way up, and there's also a cafeteria up there🤩🌞 anyone whos been? If not, whos going?🙌🏼 #Norway #Sunset

node.text: Waiting for all the comments about "how it's way too shallow to dive here"😂 The water level in the lake is so low I can dive from the ground😁🐳 swipe to the last video to see how it looks! Pretty cool if you ask me😎🐳 still no rain in sight, and water temp is probably 17-18 degrees! SO NICE💙 #Gopro #Norway #Stillsummer

node.text: Hoddevika in my 💙 !! The waves were smaller than expected- so we rented some proper longboards and had SO much fun playing with mini waves for three hours straight🤩🌸 doesn't make it any worse that it looks like a movie scene from a fairytale either🦋 anyone else that has been here?😄 #Surf #Norway #Hoddevik

node.text:
HEY! want to take photos like this? Here's a little skateboard speed-effect tutorial for you🤩
•Gopro on a selfie stick
•Timelapse mode 0.5sec
•Iso MAX 100
•ND filter to put outside of the lens if it's bright outside
•ND filter is not needed if it's somewhat darker outside
•Ride something stable such as skateboard, bike, car or something else with speed
•Go at least about 20km/h, the faster the better
•Use clarity and dehaze effect in Lightroom😎
•Have fun🥳🌞🌸
